  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WELCOME TO DUSTWIND, A POST-APOCALYPTIC TACTICS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/8115aa81709a0875f2a2d63cd079b64b.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/8115aa81709a0875f2a2d63cd079b64b.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/8115aa81709a0875f2a2d63cd079b64b.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Civilization is gone. The wasteland is all that’s left. In Dustwind, survival depends on quick thinking, smart tactics, and making the most of your character build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SINGLE-PLAYER STORY CAMPAIGNS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LAST RESORT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/b04cafc4a1db62055770f8fc1fc6bb1b.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play a nameless heroine left for dead after a violent ambush. Fight your way towards revenge and rescue someone very important to you. Survival demands patience, tactics, and smart use of every weapon at your disposal. As a side effect, you end up founding a new stronghold of hope in the brutal wastelands. Not bad!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/17a2d2db99e58795a5c85cc066f6bc82.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/17a2d2db99e58795a5c85cc066f6bc82.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/17a2d2db99e58795a5c85cc066f6bc82.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this campaign, 16 missions and around 10 hours of gameplay await you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TWO FRIENDS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/867a2b3c6c7a8ccf237724ff20d48b57.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/867a2b3c6c7a8ccf237724ff20d48b57.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/867a2b3c6c7a8ccf237724ff20d48b57.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A separate mini-campaign where you and Bob make your way toward the Last Resort camp. Expect unexpected obstacles, hard fights, and no easy roads. Buckle up and get moving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLAYER & CO-OP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/fda574aee2c153285dd2eec227b0bde2.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/fda574aee2c153285dd2eec227b0bde2.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/fda574aee2c153285dd2eec227b0bde2.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into multiple game modes: play solo, dominate co-op missions with your friends, or beat them in competitive modes. The apocalypse is better when shared!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/54da238b37fcead06c49d2f4eb39ff67.avif?t=1770813953\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PAUSE, COMMAND, EXECUTE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/6d50771a7ba9c4fb8ba8a263eb79d924.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/6d50771a7ba9c4fb8ba8a263eb79d924.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/6d50771a7ba9c4fb8ba8a263eb79d924.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat runs in real time, but you can pause at any moment to issue precise orders. Turn panic into strategy and chaos into control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY AS A DOG</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/a38e2262f3123a85957d7209db7dc67b.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/a38e2262f3123a85957d7209db7dc67b.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/a38e2262f3123a85957d7209db7dc67b.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dogs can throw grenades and lay mines, deploy turrets and barricades, drive vehicles, fire mounted guns, heal allies (bring your DOGtor!), repair equipment, and rip enemies apart. Wuff!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/5fe0600bc0a901510beb3c90d823c08b.avif?t=1770813953\" width=1200 height=674 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE YOUR GEAR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/149ae4264a4e95b5dcccc33fc323a4f1.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/149ae4264a4e95b5dcccc33fc323a4f1.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/149ae4264a4e95b5dcccc33fc323a4f1.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More gun = more fun</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DESIGN YOUR SQUAD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/db97b5e59488c1a743925425a59bc4af.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/db97b5e59488c1a743925425a59bc4af.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/db97b5e59488c1a743925425a59bc4af.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your characters with Dustwind's flexible system. Build specialists or generalists to match your tactical style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAP EDITOR & WORKSHOP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/575c6f576b6acc028dd071f0c9c1f5b9.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/575c6f576b6acc028dd071f0c9c1f5b9.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/575c6f576b6acc028dd071f0c9c1f5b9.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own missions, stories, and multiplayer maps using the powerful map editor. Share your creations with the community through Steam Workshop.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WELCOME TO DUSTWIND, A POST-APOCALYPTIC TACTICS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/8115aa81709a0875f2a2d63cd079b64b.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/8115aa81709a0875f2a2d63cd079b64b.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/8115aa81709a0875f2a2d63cd079b64b.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Civilization is gone. The wasteland is all that’s left. In Dustwind, survival depends on quick thinking, smart tactics, and making the most of your character build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SINGLE-PLAYER STORY CAMPAIGNS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LAST RESORT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/b04cafc4a1db62055770f8fc1fc6bb1b.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play a nameless heroine left for dead after a violent ambush. Fight your way towards revenge and rescue someone very important to you. Survival demands patience, tactics, and smart use of every weapon at your disposal. As a side effect, you end up founding a new stronghold of hope in the brutal wastelands. Not bad!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/17a2d2db99e58795a5c85cc066f6bc82.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/17a2d2db99e58795a5c85cc066f6bc82.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/17a2d2db99e58795a5c85cc066f6bc82.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this campaign, 16 missions and around 10 hours of gameplay await you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TWO FRIENDS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/867a2b3c6c7a8ccf237724ff20d48b57.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/867a2b3c6c7a8ccf237724ff20d48b57.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/867a2b3c6c7a8ccf237724ff20d48b57.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A separate mini-campaign where you and Bob make your way toward the Last Resort camp. Expect unexpected obstacles, hard fights, and no easy roads. Buckle up and get moving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLAYER & CO-OP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/fda574aee2c153285dd2eec227b0bde2.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/fda574aee2c153285dd2eec227b0bde2.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/fda574aee2c153285dd2eec227b0bde2.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into multiple game modes: play solo, dominate co-op missions with your friends, or beat them in competitive modes. The apocalypse is better when shared!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/54da238b37fcead06c49d2f4eb39ff67.avif?t=1770813953\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PAUSE, COMMAND, EXECUTE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/6d50771a7ba9c4fb8ba8a263eb79d924.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/6d50771a7ba9c4fb8ba8a263eb79d924.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/6d50771a7ba9c4fb8ba8a263eb79d924.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat runs in real time, but you can pause at any moment to issue precise orders. Turn panic into strategy and chaos into control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY AS A DOG</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/a38e2262f3123a85957d7209db7dc67b.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/a38e2262f3123a85957d7209db7dc67b.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/a38e2262f3123a85957d7209db7dc67b.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dogs can throw grenades and lay mines, deploy turrets and barricades, drive vehicles, fire mounted guns, heal allies (bring your DOGtor!), repair equipment, and rip enemies apart. Wuff!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/5fe0600bc0a901510beb3c90d823c08b.avif?t=1770813953\" width=1200 height=674 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE YOUR GEAR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/149ae4264a4e95b5dcccc33fc323a4f1.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/149ae4264a4e95b5dcccc33fc323a4f1.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/149ae4264a4e95b5dcccc33fc323a4f1.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More gun = more fun</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DESIGN YOUR SQUAD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/db97b5e59488c1a743925425a59bc4af.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/db97b5e59488c1a743925425a59bc4af.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/db97b5e59488c1a743925425a59bc4af.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your characters with Dustwind's flexible system. Build specialists or generalists to match your tactical style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAP EDITOR & WORKSHOP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/575c6f576b6acc028dd071f0c9c1f5b9.poster.avif?t=1770813953\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/575c6f576b6acc028dd071f0c9c1f5b9.webm?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600460/extras/575c6f576b6acc028dd071f0c9c1f5b9.mp4?t=1770813953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own missions, stories, and multiplayer maps using the powerful map editor. Share your creations with the community through Steam Workshop.</p>",
